# VectorSketch - Infinite Canvas POC

This directory contains a complete C++ proof-of-concept for an infinite canvas vector sketching application, similar to the Concepts app.

## 📁 Project Files

- **QUICKSTART.md** - Start here! Installation and basic usage
- **README.md** - Full documentation and technical details
- **ARCHITECTURE.md** - Deep dive into system design and implementation
- **CMakeLists.txt** - Build configuration
- **build.sh** - Convenient build script
- **include/** - Header files
- **src/** - Implementation files

## 🚀 Get Started

1. Install dependencies (see QUICKSTART.md)
2. Build: `./build.sh`
3. Run: `./build/VectorSketch`

## ✨ Features

- Stroke sampling with pressure/tilt data
- Bézier curve smoothing (Catmull-Rom)
- GPU-accelerated rendering (OpenGL)
- Infinite canvas with pan/zoom
- Real-time performance

Happy sketching! 🎨
